# ✅ 6️⃣ DamageCalculator

```dart
class DamageCalculator {
  double calculate({
    required double casterAttack,
    required double targetDefense,
    required double skillMultiplier,
    required ElementType element,
    required ElementType targetElement,
  }) {
    double base = casterAttack * skillMultiplier;

    double defenseReduction =
        1 - (targetDefense / (targetDefense + 100));

    double elementMultiplier =
        ElementSystem.getMultiplier(element, targetElement);

    return base * defenseReduction * elementMultiplier;
  }
}
```

